现象：每次上线重启机器之后，定时任务处理某个业务总会出现异常java.lang.ClassCastException: com.alibaba.fastjson.JSONObject cannot be cast to com.jiedaibao.umg.consumer.third.p2proute.rsp.PrtUnBindRsp
